                    "frequency": "once per day",
                    "trigger": "A creature you can sense within 60 feet would die or be destroyed",
                    "effect": "You prevent the target from dying or being destroyed and restore to the target 6d8+24 Hit Points. This effect can prevent a death effect or *disintegrate* from slaying a target. The amount of healing granted increases to 7d8+28 if you're at least 15th level, 8d8+32 if you're at least 17th level, and 9d8+36 if you're at least 19th level.",
